Package: RcurlAWS
Type: Package
Title: Interface for R to AWS focused on credential management and generic API requests.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-04-14
Authors@R: person("Alonzo", "Barnett", email = "alonzo.r.barnett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Aws Root and Temporary credential management implemented using R6  
    classes. STS is used to generate temporary credentials.  Provides functionality  
    to authorize API requests and a high-level function (awsRestRequest) as a generic request handler.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: RCurl, digest, R6
